  <body>
    <div id="rootContainer">
      <div id="hAndMContainer">
        <header>
          <div id="logoAndNav">
            <a href="/"
              ><img
                id="logo"
                src="../public/android-chrome-192x192.png"
                alt="fix logo"
            /></a>
            <%-include("partials/header.ejs")-%>
          </div>
          <hr />
          <h1>THE GUIDELINES</h1>
        </header>
        <main id="guideContainer">
          <P
            ><strong>Fix</strong> is a perfect to-do-listing application that
            provides you with a perfect service to record and manage your daily
            tasks effectively.
          </P>
          <h2>
            Follow the guidelines below to have the best experience using the
            app.
          </h2>
          <ol id="guidelines">
            <li>
                You must <strong>signup</strong> to start using the application.
            </li>
            <li>
              When signing up, use a unique username with a password not less
              than 8 characters.
            </li>
            <li>
              If your desired username is already taking by another user, you
              will get the message: <strong>"user alredy exist"</strong>.
              So, you will have to choose another username.
            </li>
            <li>
              Ensure you keep your password written and saved in a secured
              place.
            </li>
            <li>
              To <strong>login</strong>, use the correct username and password as used when
              signing up. Else, you will get an error message.
            </li>
            <li>
              In your dashboard, add "what to do" to your
              list by clicking on the
              <strong>create_task</strong> button.
            </li>
            <li>
              When a task is completed , click the
              <strong>pending</strong> button to change the state to
              <strong>completed</strong>.
            </li>
            <li>
                A task in a "completed" state can be changed back to pending if realized not completed by clicking on the <strong>completed</strong> button.
            </li>
            <li>
              Make sure you delete completed tasks to free your tasks memory.
            </li>
            <li>Logout from the app when done to secure your informations.</li>
          </ol>
          <a id="anchor" href="/signup">Get statrted</a>
        </main>
      </div>
      <footer>
        <p>
          Send us a mail &rBarr;
          <a href="mailto:maito4me@gmail.com"
            ><img id="gmail" src="../public/gmail_image.jfif" alt="gmail image"
          /></a>
        </p>
        <%-include("partials/footer.ejs")-%>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
